---
title: Honey Haloumi & Chipotle Slaw Bowl with Fajita-Style Veggies & Garlic Aioli
description: Let’s fill the bowl to the brim with salty golden slices of haloumi, a pan-fried sweetcorn and a chipotle sauce slaw
with a hit of lime to add a dash of zest and tang. Tonight will be bursting with both colour and flavour.

